/* ───────────────────── CONTACT ───────────────────── */
const FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT = "https://formspree.io/f/maqqnoen";
const REPORT_ENDPOINT = "https://formspree.io/f/maqqqvog";

/* ───────────────────── REPORT A BROKEN MACHINE ───────────────────── */
const ReportIssue = () => {
    const [form, setForm] = useState({ location: "", issue_type: "", details: "", contact: "", company: "" });
    const [status, setStatus] = useState({ state: "idle", msg: "" });
    const update = (k) => (e) => setForm({ ...form, [k]: e.target.value });

    const submit = async (e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        if (form.company) {
            setStatus({ state: "success", msg: "Report received. Thanks!" });
            return;
        }
        setStatus({ state: "loading", msg: "" });
        try {
            const res = await fetch(REPORT_ENDPOINT, {
                method: "POST",
                headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json", Accept: "application/json" },
                body: JSON.stringify({
                    machine_location: form.location,
                    issue_type: form.issue_type,
                    details: form.details,
                    contact: form.contact,
                    _subject: `⚠️ Machine issue — ${form.issue_type || "unspecified"}`,
                }),
            });
            if (!res.ok) {
                const data = await res.json().catch(() => ({}));
                throw new Error(data?.errors?.[0]?.message || "Couldn't send the report. Try again?");
            }
            setStatus({ state: "success", msg: "Report received. We're on it — thanks for letting us know." });
            setForm({ location: "", issue_type: "", details: "", contact: "", company: "" });
        } catch (err) {
            setStatus({ state: "error", msg: err.message || "Couldn't send the report. Try again?" });
        }
    };

    return (
        <section id="report" className="px-5 lg:px-10 py-24" style={{ background: "var(--snack-mint)" }} data-testid="report-section">
            <div className="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-10 items-start">
                <div className="lg:col-span-2">
                    <span className="sticker" style={{ background: "#fff" }}><AlertTriangle size={14}/> Something&apos;s off?</span>
                    <h2 className="font-display font-bold mt-5" style={{ fontSize: "clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem)" }}>Report a<br/>broken machine.</h2>
                    <p className="font-display mt-5 opacity-80 max-w-md">Snack stuck? Machine won&apos;t take payment? Screen off? Tell us where the machine is and what happened — we&apos;ll be on it fast.</p>
                    <div className="mt-8 font-mono text-sm space-y-2 opacity-80">
                        <div className="flex items-center gap-2"><ShieldCheck size={16}/> Monitored 24/7</div>
                        <div className="flex items-center gap-2"><Wrench size={16}/> Response within 24 hrs</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <form onSubmit={submit} action={REPORT_ENDPOINT} method="POST" className="lg:col-span-3 card-brutal p-6 md:p-10 space-y-4" data-testid="report-form">
                    <input required name="machine_location" value={form.location} onChange={update("location")} placeholder="Machine location (address or building name)" className="field" data-testid="report-location" />
                    <select required name="issue_type" value={form.issue_type} onChange={update("issue_type")} className="field" data-testid="report-issue-type">
                        <option value="">What&apos;s going wrong?</option>
                        <option>Item stuck in machine</option>
                        <option>Won&apos;t accept payment</option>
                        <option>Wrong item dispensed</option>
                        <option>Machine won&apos;t power on</option>
                        <option>Refund needed</option>
                        <option>Something else</option>
                    </select>
                    <textarea required name="details" value={form.details} onChange={update("details")} rows={4} placeholder="What happened? (Slot number, amount charged, anything useful.)" className="field resize-none" data-testid="report-details" />
                    <input name="contact" value={form.contact} onChange={update("contact")} placeholder="Your email or phone (optional — for refund/follow-up)" className="field" data-testid="report-contact" />
                    <input type="text" name="company" tabIndex={-1} autoComplete="off" value={form.company} onChange={update("company")} aria-hidden="true" style={{ position: "absolute", left: "-10000px", width: 1, height: 1, opacity: 0 }} data-testid="report-honeypot" />
                    <div className="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 pt-2">
                        <button type="submit" disabled={status.state === "loading"} className="btn-brutal btn-brutal--cherry" data-testid="report-submit">
                            {status.state === "loading" ? "Sending…" : "Send report"} <ArrowRight size={18} />
                        </button>
                        {status.state === "success" && <span className="font-mono text-sm font-bold" data-testid="report-success" style={{ color: "var(--snack-ink)" }}>✓ {status.msg}</span>}
                        {status.state === "error" && <span className="font-mono text-sm text-[var(--snack-cherry)] font-bold" data-testid="report-error">✗ {status.msg}</span>}
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>
    );
};

/* ───────────────────── CONTACT ───────────────────── */

const Contact = () => {
    const [form, setForm] = useState({ name: "", email: "", location: "", location_type: "", message: "", company: "" });
    const [status, setStatus] = useState({ state: "idle", msg: "" });

    const update = (k) => (e) => setForm({ ...form, [k]: e.target.value });

    const submit = async (e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        // Honeypot — silently drop if filled
        if (form.company) {
            setStatus({ state: "success", msg: "Got it! We'll be in touch soon." });
            return;
        }
        setStatus({ state: "loading", msg: "" });
        try {
            const res = await fetch(FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT, {
                method: "POST",
                headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json", Accept: "application/json" },
                body: JSON.stringify({
                    name: form.name,
                    email: form.email,
                    location: form.location,
                    location_type: form.location_type,
                    message: form.message,
                    _subject: `New Snackabot inquiry — ${form.name}`,
                }),
            });
            if (!res.ok) {
                const data = await res.json().catch(() => ({}));
                const msg = data?.errors?.[0]?.message || "Something went wrong. Try again?";
                throw new Error(msg);
            }
            setStatus({ state: "success", msg: "Got it! We'll be in touch soon." });
            setForm({ name: "", email: "", location: "", location_type: "", message: "", company: "" });
        } catch (err) {
            setStatus({ state: "error", msg: err.message || "Something went wrong. Try again?" });
        }
    };

    return (
        <section id="contact" className="px-5 lg:px-10 py-24" data-testid="contact-section">
            <div className="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-10 items-start">
                <div className="lg:col-span-2">
                    <span className="sticker"><Cookie size={14}/> Get Snackabot</span>
                    <h2 className="font-display font-bold mt-5" style={{ fontSize: "clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem)" }}>Let&apos;s put a<br/>machine somewhere.</h2>
                    <p className="font-display mt-5 opacity-80 max-w-md">Drop your details. We&apos;ll review your spot and reach out within 48 hours with a placement plan and the bonus offer.</p>
                    <div className="mt-8 space-y-3 font-mono text-sm">
                        <div className="flex items-center gap-2"><MapPin size={16}/> Providence, RI</div>
                        <div className="flex items-center gap-2"><Twitter size={16}/> @snackabot</div>
                        <div className="flex items-center gap-2"><Instagram size={16}/> @snackabot</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <form onSubmit={submit} action={FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT} method="POST" className="lg:col-span-3 card-brutal p-6 md:p-10 space-y-4" data-testid="contact-form">
                    <div className="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <input required name="name" value={form.name} onChange={update("name")} placeholder="Your name" className="field" data-testid="contact-name" />
                        <input required type="email" name="email" value={form.email} onChange={update("email")} placeholder="Email" className="field" data-testid="contact-email" />
                    </div>
                    <input name="location" value={form.location} onChange={update("location")} placeholder="Address or neighborhood (Providence)" className="field" data-testid="contact-location" />
                    <select name="location_type" value={form.location_type} onChange={update("location_type")} className="field" data-testid="contact-location-type">
                        <option value="">What kind of spot?</option>
                        <option>Office</option>
                        <option>Apartment building</option>
                        <option>Laundromat</option>
                        <option>Gym / Studio</option>
                        <option>Other commercial space</option>
                    </select>
                    <textarea required name="message" value={form.message} onChange={update("message")} rows={4} placeholder="Tell us about the spot — foot traffic, hours, anything else." className="field resize-none" data-testid="contact-message" />
                    {/* Honeypot — hidden from real users, bots fill it and we drop the submission */}
                    <input type="text" name="company" tabIndex={-1} autoComplete="off" value={form.company} onChange={update("company")} aria-hidden="true" style={{ position: "absolute", left: "-10000px", width: 1, height: 1, opacity: 0 }} data-testid="contact-honeypot" />
                    <div className="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 pt-2">
                        <button type="submit" disabled={status.state === "loading"} className="btn-brutal" data-testid="contact-submit">
                            {status.state === "loading" ? "Sending…" : "Send message"} <ArrowRight size={18} />
                        </button>
                        {status.state === "success" && <span className="font-mono text-sm text-[var(--snack-mint)] font-bold" data-testid="contact-success">✓ {status.msg}</span>}
                        {status.state === "error" && <span className="font-mono text-sm text-[var(--snack-cherry)] font-bold" data-testid="contact-error">✗ {status.msg}</span>}
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>
    );
};

